choose_words
Disk World creator help
choose_words

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
choose_words -  This function selects word replacements for #n in the text.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void choose_words(mixed label,
mixed choice)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^label%^RESET%^ - Situation label to choose for
%^BOLD%^choice%^RESET%^ - A random seed (integer) or
              a set of pairs exactly the same as the second
              argument to replace.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/basic/situation_changer.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function selects word replacements for #n in the text.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
     choose_words( "frog", ({ "#1", "tadpole", "#2", "pond" }));

.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
replace
.EP

